             if (getThreadId() == i) threadCommSlave.gatherArrayProcess
        process i send data interval [sendfroms[i], sendtos[i]) to root process, placed in the same positions, s.t. sendfroms[i] ≤ sendtos[i], sendfroms[i] ≥ sendtos[i-1]
        Parameters:
